        "subject": "LU-19465 ec: add erasure code as a separate library",
        "message": "LU-19465 ec: add erasure code as a separate library\n\nIt contains the plain-C version of the upstream library taken at version\nv2.31.0-104-ge677f66\nThe files are mostly un-modified to make it easy to verify and compare\nthem to upstream, or just dropping in new/updated versions when\nrequired.\n\nSplit the kernel module into a wrapper, ec_kmod.c, and the actual\nerasure code, ec_base.c.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Ronnie Sahlberg <rsahlberg@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: Ife875ec8c5c3a9d66f34a2cb96f452d84ce9c1ce\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/62087\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Patrick Farrell <pfarrell@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@dilger.ca>\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
      },
